text: Ratu Wiliame Maivalili Katonivere (born 20 April 1964) is a Fijian chief and politician who was the president of Fiji from 2021 until 2024. He has also been the chief of Macuata Province since 2013, replacing his older brother Aisea Katonivere. He also played a role in conservation initiatives of Fiji's Great Sea Reef. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Fiji Category:Current national leaders
